# HTTP response headers for kubernetes.recipes
#
# Format: Netlify / Cloudflare Pages "_headers" file.
#
# IMPORTANT: GitHub Pages (the current host — `server: GitHub.com`) does NOT
# support custom response headers, so this file is INERT on GitHub Pages. It
# takes effect only when the site is served by, or proxied through, a
# header-capable layer:
#   - Cloudflare Pages or Netlify (consumed at build/deploy), or
#   - Cloudflare in front of GitHub Pages (proxied DNS) using Transform Rules /
#     Response Header Rules mirroring the values below.
#
# These headers resolve the audit's two largest findings:
#   - OTHER_MISSING_HSTS_HEADER       (Strict-Transport-Security)
#   - OTHER_MISSING_OR_WEAK_CSP       (Content-Security-Policy as an HTTP header)
# plus clickjacking, MIME-sniffing, referrer-leak, and feature-policy hardening.
#
# The CSP mirrors the meta CSP in src/layouts/Layout.astro. Keep them in sync.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://*.clarity.ms https://luca-berton.kit.com https://f.convertkit.com https://app.convertkit.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://luca-berton.kit.com; img-src 'self' data: https: blob:; font-src 'self' data: https:; connect-src 'self' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://*.google-analytics.com https://*.analytics.google.com https://*.clarity.ms https://luca-berton.kit.com https://f.convertkit.com https://app.convertkit.com; frame-src https://luca-berton.kit.com https://www.youtube.com; form-action 'self' https://app.convertkit.com; frame-ancestors 'none'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'

# Keep the sample PDF (a gated lead magnet) out of search indexes.
/KubernetesRecipes-sample.pdf
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow

# Long-cache fingerprinted build assets.
/_astro/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
